('Bench Dips',2,'Lower your body straight down.'),
('Bench Dips',3,'Slowly press back up to the starting point.'),
('Bench Dips',4,'TIP: Make this harder by raising your feet off the floor and adding weight.'),
('Biceps Stretch Variation Five',1,'Stand upright with your feet shoulder width apart.'),
('Biceps Stretch Variation Five',2,'Raise your arms out to your sides, bringing them up to shoulder level.'),
('Biceps Stretch Variation Five',3,'Rotate your palms so they are facing the ceiling.'),
('Biceps Stretch Variation Five',4,'Then, change direction and rotate the arms as much as you can.'),
