('Biceps Stretch Variation One',2,'Place your hand on the wall, fingers pointing away from you.'),
('Biceps Stretch Variation One',3,'Gently lean forward, keeping your hand stationary.'),
('Biceps Stretch Variation One',4,'Repeat with the other arm.'),
('Biceps Stretch Variation Three',1,'Bend your arm at the elbow, raising your hand to your shoulder.'),
('Biceps Stretch Variation Three',2,'Using your other hand, stretch the arm down to its full extent.'),
('Biceps Stretch Variation Two',1,'Stand facing the wall, an arm\'s width away.'),
('Biceps Stretch Variation Two',2,'Place your hand on the wall with your fingers pointing down.'),
('Biceps Stretch Variation Two',3,'Lean slightly into the wall to feel the stretch in your bicep.'),
