('Bosu Ball Pike Pushup',2,'Lower the head towards the ground, then push back up.'),
('Bosu Ball Pike Pushup',3,'Keep legs straight and hips elevated throughout.'),
('Bosu Ball Pike Shrug',1,'Place toes on Bosu, hands on the floor.'),
('Bosu Ball Pike Shrug',2,'Pike hips up, shrug shoulders, engage core.'),
