('Cable External Rotation',2,'Rotate your arm outward, keeping your elbow stable.'),
('Cable Goblet Squat',1,'Start with a straight bar or easy bar attachment .'),
('Cable Goblet Squat',2,'Get your elbows directly underneath the bar, squat straight up and then walk back a few steps.'),
('Cable Goblet Squat',3,'Break at your knees and hips to initiate the squat. Make sure you maintain a flat back.'),
('Cable Goblet Squat',4,'Squat all the way back to a standing position.'),
