('Forearms Stretch Variation One',2,'Take one step forward and straighten your arm slowly to extend your bicep.'),
('Forearms Stretch Variation One',3,'Hold at the peak of the stretch.'),
('Forearms Stretch Variation One',4,'Return to starting position.'),
