('Glutes Stretch Variation One',2,'Fully extend your leg and arm.'),
('Glutes Stretch Variation One',3,'Hold at the peak of the stretch, then slowly return to starting position.'),
('Glutes Stretch Variation One',4,'Switch sides and repeat.'),
