('Glutes Stretch Variation Three',2,'Hold your left leg with both hands and slowly rotate your hips to the right hand side.'),
('Glutes Stretch Variation Three',3,'Hold at the peak of the stretch, then slowly return to starting position.'),
('Glutes Stretch Variation Three',4,'Switch sides and repeat.'),
