('Half Neck Rolls',2,'Drop your chin to your chest and roll your head to the right, bringing your right ear towards your right shoulder.'),
('Half Neck Rolls',3,'Slowly roll your head back to center, then over to the left so that your left ear is close to your left shoulder.'),
('Half Neck Rolls',4,'Repeat the movement from side to side, keeping your shoulders relaxed and breathing deeply.'),
('Hamstring Bridge Isometric Open Angle',1,'Lie on your back with knees slightly bent and heels dug in.'),
