('Hamstring Bridge With Elevated Legs Box Bilateral',3,'Push through your heels into the box, lifting your hips up to the point where there is a straight line from your chest to your knees.'),
('Hamstring Bridge With Elevated Legs Box Unilateral',1,'Lie on your back. Place one heel on a box or bench, having a 90° angle at hip and knee.'),
