('Hamstrings Stretch Variation Four',2,'Reach forward to try and touch your toes. Reach as far forward as you can go.'),
('Hamstrings Stretch Variation Four',3,'Hold the stretch for a few seconds then return to starting position.'),
('Hamstrings Stretch Variation One',1,'Lie down with your legs reaching up the wall. your bum should be slightly off the floor.'),
('Hamstrings Stretch Variation One',2,'Bend one leg and leave the other outstretched.'),
('Hamstrings Stretch Variation One',3,'Push your thigh towards the wall.'),
('Hamstrings Stretch Variation One',4,'Hold the stretch for a few seconds then return to starting position.'),
