('Hamstrings Stretch Variation Three',2,'Reach forward to touch the toes of the outstretched leg.'),
('Hamstrings Stretch Variation Three',3,'Hold the stretch for a few seconds then return to starting position.'),
('Hamstrings Stretch Variation Two',1,'Stand with one foot in front of the other.'),
('Hamstrings Stretch Variation Two',2,'Bend your rear leg as much as you can, keeping the front leg straight.'),
('Hamstrings Stretch Variation Two',3,'Hold the stretch for a few seconds then return to starting position.'),
('Hand Side Plank',1,'Press your hand into the ground and pick up your hip off the ground.'),
('Hand Side Plank',2,'Open your chest and maintain this position for the allotted amount of time.'),
