('Horizontal Hack Squat',2,'Place feet shoulder-width apart on the platform.'),
('Horizontal Hack Squat',3,'Press through your heels to the starting position, keeping your core engaged. Repeat for desired reps and sets.'),
('Hundred',1,'Lie supine, legs tabletop or extended, arms reaching long by sides.'),
('Hundred',2,'Lift head and shoulders, engage core, gaze toward thighs.'),
('Hundred',3,'Pump arms vigorously, inhaling five counts, exhaling five counts.'),
('Hundred',4,'Maintain stable torso and strong abdominals for one hundred counts.'),
('Hundred Straight Legs',1,'Lie supine, legs tabletop or extended, arms reaching long by sides.'),
('Hundred Straight Legs',2,'Lift head and shoulders, engage core, gaze toward thighs.'),
('Hundred Straight Legs',3,'Pump arms vigorously, inhaling five counts, exhaling five counts.'),
('Hundred Straight Legs',4,'Maintain stable torso and strong abdominals for one hundred counts.'),
('In And Out Jump Squat',1,'Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.'),
('In And Out Jump Squat',2,'Start by doing a regular squat, then engage your core and jump up explosively.'),
('In And Out Jump Squat',3,'Narrow your stance while in the air, and land softly. Go directly into another rep.'),
